Supply Ducts

Supply Duct Area

sD1A = sD1W * sD1H; 
sD2A = sD2W * sD2H; 
sD3A = sD3W * sD3H; 
sDT = sD4A + sD5A + sD6A + sD3A + sD2A + sD1A; 
sDTcfmMax = sDT * 6; 
sDTcfmRec = sDT * 4.5;
sDTdA = (acCFM / 4.5) - sDT;
sD4dr = sD4d / 2
sD5dr = sD5d / 2
sD6dr = sD6d / 2
sD4A = sD4dr * sD4dr * pi
sD5A = sD5dr * sD5dr * pi
